headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid HIG and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Hartford has followed the market’s trajectory closely, rising in tandem with the S&P 500 over the past six months. The stock has climbed by 9.5% to $142.15 per share while the index has gained 6%.
